            <title>[SHIRO-142] Jetty throws an IllegalStateException after redirect in AuthorizationFilter</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SHIRO-142</link>
                <project id="12310950" key="SHIRO">Shiro</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Jetty throws an IllegalStateException because if onAccessDenied&lt;br/&gt;
